{"id":4877,"date":"2023-07-31T06:09:50","date_gmt":"2023-07-31T06:09:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/pureplumbingsolutionsca.com\/?p=4877"},"modified":"2024-05-14T04:30:30","modified_gmt":"2024-05-14T04:30:30","slug":"four-common-drain-issues-that-require-a-professional-plumber","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/pureplumbingsolutionsca.com\/four-common-drain-issues-that-require-a-professional-plumber\/","title":{"rendered":"Four Common Drain Issues that Require a Professional Plumber"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"4877\" class=\"elementor elementor-4877\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4b24e10 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-items-middle\" data-id=\"4b24e10\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-544d6df\" data-id=\"544d6df\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d3e0d1a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d3e0d1a\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d257184\" data-id=\"d257184\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-07edfab elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"07edfab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_center   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Blog<\/h2><\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9df2f7e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9df2f7e\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-da96168\" data-id=\"da96168\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b795cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"1b795cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_center   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Four Common Drain Issues that Require a Professional Plumber<\/h2><div class=\"ekit_heading_separetor_wraper ekit_heading_elementskit-border-divider\"><div class=\"elementskit-border-divider\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dbd0631 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dbd0631\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several drain issues that may arise in a household, and while some can be addressed by homeowners themselves, certain situations require the expertise of a <\/span><b>professional plumber for Drain Issues<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Here are four common drain issues that usually need the attention of a professional:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-865ffd6 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"865ffd6\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-4970e5c\" data-id=\"4970e5c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91f357d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"91f357d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Persistent Clogs: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When a drain gets clogged frequently and standard home remedies like plunging or using drain cleaners don&#8217;t seem to solve the problem, there might be a more extensive blockage deep within the pipes. Professional plumbers have the tools and knowledge to locate and remove stubborn clogs safely without causing damage to the plumbing system.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Slow Draining:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> If you notice water taking an unusually long time to drain from sinks, bathtubs, or showers, it could be a sign of a partial blockage or buildup of debris within the pipes. While minor slow draining might be resolved with DIY methods, consistent or severe slow drainage may indicate a more severe issue that requires professional intervention.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-0a6b5f7\" data-id=\"0a6b5f7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fac39e9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fac39e9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Foul Odors:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Persistent unpleasant smells emanating from drains suggest a potential problem within the plumbing system. It could be due to rotting food particles, sewage backup, or a dried-out P-trap (the U-shaped bend in the pipe designed to prevent sewer odors from escaping). A professional plumber can identify the source of the odor and provide the appropriate solution.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Water Backups:<\/b><span> Backups can occur in various fixtures, such as sinks, toilets, or showers. When water backs up or overflows, it may be a sign of a severe blockage or a problem with the sewer line. Dealing with sewer line issues requires specialized equipment and knowledge, making it essential to seek professional help<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55894a5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"55894a5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In general, if a drain issue persists despite attempts to resolve it using simple remedies, or if the problem affects multiple drains throughout the house, it is best to call a professional plumber. Trying to force DIY solutions on complex plumbing problems may lead to more damage and higher repair costs in the long run. <\/span><b>Professional plumbers <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">have the training and experience to diagnose and fix drain issues efficiently and effectively, ensuring the plumbing system is back in proper working condition.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Blog Four Common Drain Issues that Require a Professional Plumber There are several drain issues that may arise in a household, and while some can be addressed by homeowners themselves, certain situations require the expertise of a professional plumber for Drain Issues. Here are four common drain issues that usually need the attention of a &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5964,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"elementor_header_footer","format":"standard","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/pureplumbingsolutionsca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4877"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/pureplumbingsolutionsca.c